Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.63,0:00:04.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.17,0:00:18.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的心就能神奇地变得坦率
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.35,0:00:23.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,背后仿佛有你的脚步声
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.52,0:00:30.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追赶了过来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.13,0:00:41.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我频频回头看着你的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.07,0:00:51.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新恋情的开始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.68,0:00:55.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是两人在不知不觉中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.52,0:01:07.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,展开看不见的爱的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.16,0:01:15.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以永远不愿分离
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.20,0:01:24.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我发誓我只爱你一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.06,0:01:38.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星期天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.79,0:01:40.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑看起来真的很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.00,0:01:44.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是约会喔，约会
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.77,0:01:48.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天，我跟学姐见面的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.30,0:01:49.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有告诉千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.84,0:01:52.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样也对不起你的老公啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.37,0:01:54.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一下子就好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.01,0:01:56.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你能躺在我身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.18,0:02:02.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.92,0:02:07.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我心里很明白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.16,0:02:09.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢的人是千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.56,0:02:14.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于初恋的人\N已经是过去的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.76,0:02:18.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.10,0:02:22.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望我能一直看到这个笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.27,0:02:28.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的钱包掉了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.25,0:02:35.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,#04冬美学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.19,0:02:38.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里，这里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.86,0:02:43.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起，有点远
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.76,0:02:45.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会，不会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.46,0:02:46.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.39,0:02:48.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的眼睛很好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.06,0:02:50.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！是海豹耶！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.73,0:02:52.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看，还有海豚！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.94,0:02:56.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.54,0:03:01.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起喔，阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.68,0:03:03.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钱包掉了的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.78,0:03:07.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为看不到海豹\N已经死心了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.55,0:03:09.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傻瓜，那不是烦恼海豹的时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.88,0:03:11.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.29,0:03:16.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你把全部的钱\N都放在我这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.73,0:03:22.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁叫你不晓得\N把钱包放到哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.10,0:03:23.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是你不好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.50,0:03:27.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.41,0:03:34.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意思是我的错咯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.78,0:03:37.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.65,0:03:38.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.75,0:03:45.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过，阿修\N我真的玩得好开心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.85,0:03:48.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一定还能再来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.32,0:03:49.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然咯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.67,0:04:02.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑，来拍张照片吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.10,0:04:06.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还没一起拍过照片吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.14,0:04:08.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想拍照
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.34,0:04:09.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.68,0:04:11.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.11,0:04:12.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.61,0:04:15.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了照片的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.92,0:04:17.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得会因此就放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.46,0:04:23.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望我还在的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.99,0:04:26.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能看着真正的我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.30,0:04:31.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望能藉由你证明我的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.20,0:04:34.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我能感觉到\N我真的存在于这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.47,0:04:43.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我相信\N我不是孤单一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.05,0:04:54.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过，今天真的运气不错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.76,0:04:55.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有接到紧急出击的通知
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.96,0:05:01.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实，我把呼叫器放在家里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.03,0:05:04.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这是我第一次约会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.30,0:05:08.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想被任何人打扰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.60,0:05:11.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.67,0:05:14.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是个坏女孩吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.88,0:05:17.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你才不是个坏女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.51,0:05:18.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.01,0:05:22.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又不是天天都有战争
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.08,0:05:23.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用在意啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.32,0:05:26.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.89,0:05:29.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定真有这种日子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.12,0:05:31.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.63,0:05:34.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪有人不约会的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.30,0:05:37.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在普通的高中女生\N每个人都在约会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.73,0:05:40.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普通的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.37,0:05:43.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊，所以你没有做错事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.27,0:05:45.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天全世界一定都很和平
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.14,0:05:46.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像这个城镇一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.68,0:05:55.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这里是我的故乡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.32,0:06:00.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界上根本没有和平了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.52,0:06:06.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在比这个更大的城市\N都会很轻易的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.96,0:06:09.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在瞬间就被毁灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.73,0:06:11.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.68,0:06:23.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实千濑的体温
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.51,0:06:27.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的低到令人鼻酸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.78,0:06:32.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她现在到底\N有多少属于“人”的部份呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.92,0:06:35.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的颈部依然如此纤细
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.82,0:06:38.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的发香依然令人心醉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.04,0:06:53.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修，对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.17,0:06:55.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像还是被找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.51,0:06:59.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我非去不可
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.72,0:07:06.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修，不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.32,0:07:07.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.72,0:07:10.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起，忍耐一下喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.73,0:07:12.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.35,0:07:38.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到底酸什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.62,0:07:39.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到底酸什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.79,0:07:41.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.56,0:07:43.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得去拿钱包
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.29,0:07:44.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.97,0:08:00.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.21,0:08:01.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钱包
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.08,0:08:04.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是来拿钱包而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.55,0:08:13.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也到了能让女人\N枕腕而睡的年纪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.55,0:08:14.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点感动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.63,0:08:18.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.46,0:08:53.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.99,0:08:55.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么要哭呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.17,0:09:00.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起，我又…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.24,0:09:03.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.04,0:09:06.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的，学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.57,0:09:07.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.91,0:09:11.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我总是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.01,0:09:13.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.58,0:09:18.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只会做出让千濑伤心的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.05,0:09:22.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明是她男朋友\N为什么总是让她哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.66,0:09:26.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都决定当她的男朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.89,0:09:30.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都决定相恋了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.07,0:09:33.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我无法保护千濑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.17,0:09:38.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑她又没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.71,0:09:40.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.34,0:09:42.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我也没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.88,0:09:46.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.18,0:09:50.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道该怎么办才好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.65,0:09:56.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.92,0:09:58.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.93,0:10:02.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听到千濑寂寞的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.14,0:10:13.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑现在\N可能也在某个地方哭泣着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.79,0:10:32.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢…好烫\N你干嘛买热的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.49,0:10:34.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,买错了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.33,0:10:37.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换成千濑\N你可能会笑着原谅她，对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.17,0:10:49.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修次，快点跟千濑做啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.38,0:10:50.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样会轻松很多喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.75,0:10:53.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个都太笨拙了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.95,0:10:57.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干嘛这么鸡婆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.55,0:11:02.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实，我觉得我很傻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.59,0:11:06.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑今天又请假了不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.19,0:11:09.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她从小身体就很虚弱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.23,0:11:10.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,念小学的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.97,0:11:15.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还曾经在东京的医院\N住院了好几个月
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.44,0:11:19.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且又笨笨的\N没有什么朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.84,0:11:22.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我答应过她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.91,0:11:25.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会一直保护她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.38,0:11:30.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论什么事我都会帮她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.95,0:11:33.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以要她打起精神来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.62,0:11:36.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个给你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.33,0:11:40.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我实在看不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.23,0:11:44.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上课的时候你也呆呆的看着\N千濑请假缺席的空位子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.00,0:11:46.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才没有看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.27,0:11:48.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正这张送给你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.07,0:11:50.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那张八百年前的照片\N别带在身上了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.84,0:11:52.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这张好好带着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.27,0:11:56.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉，我会的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.04,0:12:00.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我的部份涂掉没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.51,0:12:34.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的啦，就这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.88,0:12:35.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.02,0:12:38.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果啊，那时候她啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.26,0:12:42.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.09,0:12:46.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能给我一点水喝？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.36,0:12:49.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.33,0:12:52.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起，我看还是酸了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.13,0:12:55.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真正的千濑妹妹耶！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.00,0:12:57.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好佩服你喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.87,0:13:00.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那一仗你打得好棒喔！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.47,0:13:02.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的好强喔，千濑妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.14,0:13:04.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.45,0:13:08.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个\N怎么可以这样对长官说话！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.88,0:13:10.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中队长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.22,0:13:12.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的部下失礼了，很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.36,0:13:16.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿铁小队长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.69,0:13:20.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的，我不是叫你\N不要叫我阿铁小队长吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.53,0:13:21.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.50,0:13:23.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷达还是无法发挥作用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.03,0:13:26.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干扰波太强了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.40,0:13:28.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ECCM也没有反应
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.60,0:13:30.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法估计还剩多少敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.27,0:13:34.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真要命，这不就等于\N是在一百年前打仗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.94,0:13:39.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才千濑中队长大发神威\N把敌人全灭了不是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.51,0:13:41.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但愿如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.28,0:13:42.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.25,0:13:44.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又在谦虚了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.92,0:13:45.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中村！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.62,0:13:49.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.09,0:13:51.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我感觉得到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.79,0:13:54.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有敌人在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.96,0:13:56.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且数量不少
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.03,0:13:59.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可能已经被包围了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.00,0:14:03.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.17,0:14:05.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会再去解决的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.44,0:14:08.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.31,0:14:09.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.78,0:14:17.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她吃的药好像有点不寻常…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.12,0:14:20.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的水
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.55,0:14:22.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你的水
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.96,0:14:26.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.23,0:14:28.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实刚才战斗的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.86,0:14:31.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我故意放走了很多敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.83,0:14:36.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的敌人实在太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.07,0:14:38.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太过用力的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.14,0:14:43.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怕一个不小心\N这个城市也会被我“那个”
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.41,0:14:47.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿淳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.35,0:14:48.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么慢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.82,0:14:49.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.52,0:14:54.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是由佳利吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.96,0:14:55.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.29,0:15:02.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛，好痛喔…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.03,0:15:05.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.37,0:15:08.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为千濑妹妹说\N他有男朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.30,0:15:11.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长得怎么样？比我帅吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.91,0:15:14.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋，别发出那种\N丢人现眼的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.84,0:15:21.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实他也谈不上帅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.45,0:15:23.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.42,0:15:24.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.55,0:15:26.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像阿铁小队长这种人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.39,0:15:27.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭小子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.09,0:15:28.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.02,0:15:30.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.56,0:15:32.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.23,0:15:34.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白痴！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.00,0:15:36.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.70,0:15:41.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你骂“白痴”的时候\N跟他有点像
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.07,0:15:42.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白痴？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.00,0:15:46.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自从我变成终极武器之后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.01,0:15:49.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就成为别人眼中的不良少女
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.54,0:15:51.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家里的人什么都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.05,0:15:53.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,经常翘课
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.71,0:15:55.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,半夜还会偷跑出去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.85,0:15:59.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家对我都已经死心了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.99,0:16:01.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本懒得管我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.22,0:16:09.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是阿修现在还会骂我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.26,0:16:11.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我笨手笨脚的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.47,0:16:15.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他动不动就会骂我“傻瓜”\N或是“你这个笨蛋”
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.60,0:16:19.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明是个武器
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.77,0:16:23.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明杀了那么多人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.61,0:16:26.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实是个坏孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.95,0:16:29.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有他还会骂我“笨蛋”
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.95,0:16:33.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他知道你是终极武器吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.96,0:16:39.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道，札幌空袭的时候\N被他看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.09,0:16:41.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每当阿修骂我的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.03,0:16:45.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使只有一瞬间\N我都会觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.03,0:16:48.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉得我还是一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.04,0:16:52.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉得我还有资格活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.97,0:16:54.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.04,0:16:59.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为你的奋战是有很意义的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.48,0:17:02.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.78,0:17:05.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.09,0:17:07.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那场战斗我差点就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.69,0:17:10.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏你奋战救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.06,0:17:16.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我奋战的…意义？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.20,0:17:20.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对…对啊！\N要不是你，我也早就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.40,0:17:21.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.44,0:17:24.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.31,0:17:27.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.97,0:17:35.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最近渐渐地可以\N控制自己的力量了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.65,0:17:39.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前一上战场\N马上就会失去意识
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.12,0:17:43.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后身体就自己动起来\N变得很恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.46,0:17:50.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前阵子国外不是有个小镇\N凭空消失了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.03,0:17:55.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有意识的话\N我会觉得很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.77,0:18:01.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过最近习惯了\N只要忍耐一下就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.14,0:18:04.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望多少能帮别人一点忙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.21,0:18:06.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么话啊，千濑妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.35,0:18:09.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你帮了很多人的说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.15,0:18:11.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也这么认为
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.22,0:18:14.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不然这国家早就…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.22,0:18:16.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了，不要说了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.82,0:18:18.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要说这些有的没的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.29,0:18:20.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有的没的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.66,0:18:22.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中队长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.13,0:18:26.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你也不要想太多\N专心作战就…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.77,0:18:27.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.90,0:18:29.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.14,0:18:33.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人已经来了，在上空盘旋着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.97,0:18:37.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌，他们是冲着我来的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.41,0:18:39.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经被锁定了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.85,0:18:40.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你们快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.78,0:18:41.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.55,0:18:42.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全体撤退！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.98,0:18:43.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.09,0:18:50.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.39,0:18:53.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.27,0:19:00.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.41,0:19:09.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说内地被炸得很惨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.21,0:19:13.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比札幌惨很多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.45,0:19:16.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是望着这么美丽的星空
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.22,0:19:19.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对无法想像那种景象
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.29,0:19:22.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这个城市真的很和平啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.46,0:19:27.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这里是我的故乡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.50,0:19:32.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么其他的地方很惨\N这只是谣言吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.30,0:19:34.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要信以为真
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.17,0:19:35.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.47,0:19:40.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我还是希望这个城市\N能够永保和平
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.77,0:19:41.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.98,0:19:46.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我奋战的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.61,0:19:51.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有意义的话\N我想保护
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.22,0:19:55.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保护爸爸、妈妈、弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.29,0:19:57.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个城市所有的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.49,0:20:06.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不，我希望靠我的力量\N尽可能保护这个星球更多的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.07,0:20:13.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么一来\N阿修会不会稍微夸奖我呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.77,0:20:17.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么一来，从那天以来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.44,0:20:20.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从我爽约的那天以来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.78,0:20:23.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一直处于的这种尴尬状态
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.75,0:20:28.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能稍微回复到以前那样呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.76,0:20:37.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然这样，我要再加油
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.57,0:20:42.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微再出一点力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.94,0:20:45.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要加油
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.61,0:20:55.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要努力奋战
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.52,0:21:06.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得先发制人才行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.33,0:21:08.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.96,0:21:12.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要保护大家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.43,0:21:16.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要让阿修夸奖我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.37,0:21:20.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经够了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.14,0:21:24.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.25,0:21:28.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.88,0:21:32.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你表现得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.62,0:21:37.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.66,0:21:41.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.13,0:21:44.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你把我杀了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.43,0:21:51.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经受不了这样的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.87,0:21:54.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的太笨了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.07,0:21:59.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是个武器\N竟然还以为能保护人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.36,0:22:13.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望心爱的人永远不变\N是愚蠢的想法吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.39,0:22:17.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是因为我太年轻的关系？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.40,0:22:21.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是千濑也还只是个高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.97,0:22:24.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才十七岁，个子小小的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.90,0:22:26.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个很普通的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.11,0:22:28.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很普通的…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.85,0:22:43.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的心中有一道裂缝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.82,0:22:50.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难以入眠的夜里总不停的叹息
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.83,0:22:59.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知不觉中黎明已悄悄到来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.44,0:23:09.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多么想听见你的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.35,0:23:13.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感受你的体温
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.52,0:23:20.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对你的思念越来越强烈
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.76,0:23:25.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泪水夺眶而出
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.47,0:23:30.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了我心爱的人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.64,0:23:36.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我仍无法忘怀你的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.88,0:23:41.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然只因一句再见
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.75,0:23:47.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就要结束一切
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.29,0:23:52.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫人感到悲哀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.97,0:24:03.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑，为什么要忍耐呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.47,0:24:05.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还只是高中生耶
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.41,0:24:07.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在谈恋爱的普通高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.74,0:24:10.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再多跟我聊一些吧，千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.84,0:24:15.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最终兵器彼女下一回\N[谎言]
